Package: selmaR
Title: R Client for the SELMA Student Management System API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Peeyoosh", "Chandra", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "pc@strategyandops.co")
Description: Provides a clean interface to the SELMA student management system
    REST API. Handles authentication, Hydra JSON-LD pagination, and data
    standardisation. Supports fetching students, enrolments, intakes,
    components, and programmes with optional RDS caching. Includes utilities
    for NZ/AU phone normalisation, SELMA date parsing, and EFTS pro-rata
    calculation for New Zealand TEOs.
